title: Czech Republic Job Vacancies
description: Job Vacancies in Czech Republic decreased to 297360 in October from 306098 in September of 2022. Job Vacancies in Czech Republic averaged 109307.83  from 1990 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 363917  in February of 2022 and a record low of 30803  in December of 2010. This page provides - Czech Republic Job Vacancies - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs
